{
  "id": "adv_event_2511_01_02",
  "title": "ひらめきの\n温泉",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカにとうちゃーく！\n帰って来ましたよ、LizNoirの第二の故郷へ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.338321781099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "いつ第二の故郷になったのよ\nまぁ、何度も渡米してアメリカにも慣れてはきたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5333333333,
      "endTime": 14.813333352299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0041949272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "今日からこっちで生活しながら新曲を完成させて\nレコーディングするんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0041949272,
      "endTime": 20.980000019000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.1708615939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "初めての海外レコーディング、楽しみです！\n……ところで、葵さんはどこですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1708615939,
      "endTime": 28.479138056399997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1041949272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんなら、あそこでぶつぶつ呟いてますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6708615939,
      "endTime": 32.1031519572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3041949272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "情熱を込める……情熱……\n歌とダンスで想いを爆発させる……爆発……爆発……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3041949272,
      "endTime": 44.0003855705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2041949272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、新曲のことでずっと悩んでますよね\n飛行機の機内でも、ああやって呟いてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2041949272,
      "endTime": 51.8723356246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0708615939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "悩むのはいいけど\n機内で爆発爆発って呟くのはやめてほしかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0708615939,
      "endTime": 58.2902265231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4810880978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "客室乗務員が葵を監視しながらひそひそ話してたの\n絶対勘違いされてたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4810880978,
      "endTime": 64.7610881169,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6470.861593899997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9519496917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、大丈夫ですか？　私に手伝えることがあれば\n迷惑だと思わずに、遠慮しないで言って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9519496917,
      "endTime": 73.0519498824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2519496917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんから迷惑を掛けられることが……\n頼ってもらえることが、私もこころも嬉しいんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2519496917,
      "endTime": 80.2270290374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4186163584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。二人のことは頼りにしてるよ\n何かあったら真っ先にみんなの力を借りるつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4186163584,
      "endTime": 88.4617227236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7852809905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今度の新曲は僕が責任を持って作り上げたいんだ\nだからまずは僕に任せてもらえないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7852809905,
      "endTime": 98.853920555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.0519476572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……いいわ。私達はいつでもそばにいるから\n助けがほしくなったら声を掛けてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0519476572,
      "endTime": 105.63893162389999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。じゃあ早速……\n空港に着いて、預けていた手荷物を受け取ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8297931987,
      "endTime": 113.7645812351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9631300925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "今見たら、これ、全然違う知らない人の荷物だったんだ\nどうしたらいいと思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9631300925,
      "endTime": 119.9464673041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1298008281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "助けがほしいって言ったのは音楽活動のことで\nそれ以外の葵のドジまでは責任持てないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1298008281,
      "endTime": 126.84041293429999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9812684057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ここ、懐かしいですね。アメリカで暮らしていた時と\n同じ部屋でまた過ごせるなんて思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0312684057,
      "endTime": 136.8355766295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.0312684057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが部屋を確保してくれたのよ\nホテル暮らしより、ここの方が気が楽だろうからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0312684057,
      "endTime": 144.01027069059998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.2011322655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがこころのマネージャー、やりおーる\nここならリラックスして過ごせそうですね、葵さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2011322655,
      "endTime": 152.3812458672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.6011322655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\nあ、ああ、そうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1677897768,
      "endTime": 157.4677897768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.6677897768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "顔つきが険しいわよ。曲作りで悩むのは分かるけど\nもう少し肩の力を抜いたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6677897768,
      "endTime": 164.9757038431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.1665654179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
